                        <div class="text-gray-300 text-sm mt-3 p-3 bg-gray-800/50 rounded border border-gray-700">
                            <strong>Returns a value</strong> (not a statement). Great for assignments, JSX, and short conditionals. Avoid nesting deeply.
                        </div>

                        <ProTip>
                            <div>✨ <strong>When to use ternary:</strong></div>
                            <div class="pl-2 border-l-2 border-yellow-500/30 space-y-0.5 mt-1">
                                <div class="font-mono text-[10px]"><span class="text-green-400">// Simple assignment ✅</span></div>
                                <div class="font-mono text-[10px]">const status = isActive ? 'online' : 'offline'</div>
                                <div class="font-mono text-[10px] mt-1"><span class="text-green-400">// JSX conditionals ✅</span></div>
                                <div class="font-mono text-[10px]">&lt;div&gt;&lbrace;isLoading ? 'Loading...' : data&rbrace;&lt;/div&gt;</div>
                                <div class="font-mono text-[10px] mt-1"><span class="text-red-400">// Avoid deep nesting ❌</span></div>
